metadata.name: First and Last Tears
metadata.description: This is a future world which I made up in my mind, when a baby getting born they don't cry or dropping any tears, where everyone’s controlled by totalitarianism, and they have a limited time to live, to create their world and become a happy person, but the terrible thing is while you’re having fun you don't know that you're in a deep dream and your body controlled for some terrible job, after your time getting over you gonna wake up from your sweet dreams and remembering a life you have never seen it, after you’re close to be a dead person your First and Last Tears getting drop from your eyes, the only tear which combined all your happiness in your dreams.
